OL,3,CMan 'forced to live in car' after
OL,4,Cspending 80% of wage to rent a room
OL,6,FA Guernsey man who lives in his car
OL,7,Fhas called on the island's government
OL,8,Fto do more to support people who are
OL,9,Fhomeless.
OL,11,FPaul Goddard says he has been sleeping
OL,12,Frough for three years after he had to
OL,13,Fmove out of a property and was refused
OL,14,Fthe financial help he needs from the
OL,15,FStates.
OL,17,FHe was offered a room to live in and
OL,18,Fraise his children by the Government
OL,19,Fbut says cost of rent was too high
OL,20,Fwithout income support which he did
OL,21,Fnot qualify for.
