OL,3,CMan 'forced to live in car' after
OL,4,Cspending 80% of wage to rent a room
OL,6,FPaul tells ITV News that he was paying
OL,7,Falmost #1,300 per month for the room
OL,8,Fwhile only earning #1,600.
OL,10,FThe States of Guernsey says income
OL,11,Fsupport is offered if "a person's
OL,12,Fhousehold income is not sufficient to
OL,13,Fmeet their needs" and cannot comment
OL,14,Fon individual cases.
OL,16,FPaul says he knows of other people in
OL,17,FGuernsey living in cars and tents due
OL,18,Fto a lack of affordable social housing
OL,19,Fand financial support.
