OL,3,CMan 'forced to live in car' after
OL,4,Cspending 80% of wage to rent a room
OL,6,FHe explains: "I've seen it quite a few
OL,7,Ftimes. There was a family living in a
OL,8,Fcar parked down at Grandes Rocques.
OL,10,F"Their baby used to wake up crying
OL,11,Fbetween two and three o'clock every
OL,12,Fnight. There were two or three cars
OL,13,Fparked down here at one stage.
OL,15,F"I've had a few friends living in
OL,16,Ftents and vehicles, it's just awful."
