OL,3,CMan 'forced to live in car' after
OL,4,Cspending 80% of wage to rent a room
OL,6,FJim Roberts, the Director of
OL,7,FGuernsey's first dedicated
OL,8,Fhomelessness charity for adults, At
OL,9,FHome in Guernsey, also says the
OL,10,FGovernment needs to do more to support
OL,11,Fpeople.
OL,13,FHe explains: "It continues to be awful
OL,14,Fand it looks like it might get worse.
OL,16,F"It's a problem that is largely
OL,17,Finvisible. That can make it more
OL,18,Fdifficult to tackle and for
OL,19,Fpoliticians to take seriously.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/10
