OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F381A1725378846
OL,3,CMan 'forced to live in car' after
OL,4,Cspending 80% of wage to rent a room
OL,6,F"The lowest earning quarter of people
OL,7,Fon the island are paying up to 78% of
OL,8,Ftheir income on rent. That is patently
OL,9,Funsustainable."
OL,11,FJim says At Home in Guernsey is
OL,12,Fworking to secure the safety of people
OL,13,Fon low incomes in the short-term by
OL,14,Fhelping maximise the amount of
OL,15,Fgovernment support they can receive
OL,16,Fand working to maintain tenancy
OL,17,Fagreements.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/10
