OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F381A1725378846
OL,3,CMan 'forced to live in car' after
OL,4,Cspending 80% of wage to rent a room
OL,6,FHowever, he believes that long-term
OL,7,Fsolutions will have to come from
OL,8,F"political will" and the
OL,9,FInfrastructure Committee's recent
OL,10,FHousing Plan update fails to address
OL,11,Fhomelessness urgently enough - work to
OL,12,Freduce it only due to begin in 2025.
OL,14,FJim wants to see immediate action to
OL,15,Fagree a statutory definition of
OL,16,Fhomelessness, to understand the exact
OL,17,Fscale of it in Guernsey and to offer
OL,18,Fmore affordable homes quicker.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/10
