OL,3,CMan 'forced to live in car' after
OL,4,Cspending 80% of wage to rent a room
OL,6,FGuernsey's Infrastructure Committee
OL,7,FPresident, Deputy Lindsay de
OL,8,FSausmarez, says: "We know there are
OL,9,Flots of different factors feeding into
OL,10,Fhomelessness.
OL,12,F"It is about availability of homes,
OL,13,Fsomething we are doing an awful lot on
OL,14,Fin the Guernsey Housing Plan.
OL,16,F"It is also about affordability and I
OL,17,Fam pleased to say affordability is
OL,18,Fmoving in the right direction,
OL,19,Fincluding for people in the private
OL,20,Frental sector who are particularly
OL,21,Fvulnerable to homelessness.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
