OL,3,CMan 'forced to live in car' after
OL,4,Cspending 80% of wage to rent a room
OL,6,F"It is also about security of tenure,
OL,7,Fit is one of the reasons people will
OL,8,Ffind themselves homeless and we are
OL,9,Fdoing a really big bit of work at the
OL,10,Fmoment on the rights and
OL,11,Fresponsibilities of landlords and
OL,12,Ftenants."
OL,14,FGuernsey States say they cannot
OL,15,Fcomment on individual cases and do not
OL,16,Fencourage people to live in tents, but
OL,17,Fif anyone informs Social Security that
OL,18,Fthey are living at a campsite and they
OL,19,Fqualify for income support, this money
OL,20,Fcan be used for a pitch fee.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/10
